⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Black
node MTG · MTG · ⟦Black:MTG:9806b0⟧

WHO   — Black — power · ambition
WHAT  — One of the five colours: sacrifice, drain, reanimation, and ruthless tutoring, on the conviction that power is the only real currency.
WHERE — MTG · MTG Arena  Framework inputs: Magic: The Gathering / MTG Arena (WotC)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because Black is Magic's honest villain that isn't a villain — the colour brave enough to say it wants to win.
HOW   — By paying any price (life, creatures, the future) to get the result, and refusing ever to be the victim.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Power is the only currency, and death is just a resource — I am not evil, only honest about what everyone wants.

